hackathon-description-text: In Austrian universities research is being conducted at higher and higher levels. Not only academics but also enterprises are starting to take notice. A lesser known fact is that much of the outcomes of this high-level research can be turned into entrepreneurial solutions to real problems. There are many hidden treasures at universities in the forms of inventions, patents, protoyteps and other technologies, all waiting for an entrepreneur to bring them to light and turn them into profitable businesses.
